OL,3,CWhy these elections are so important
OL,5,FToday's elections could be the most
OL,6,Fconsequential of my lifetime, outside
OL,7,Fof a general election. Here's why.
OL,9,FFirst, if they are as catastrophic for
OL,10,FLabour as some polls indicate, they
OL,11,Fmay send Labour MPs into paroxysms of
OL,12,Fdespair, and set in train a challenge
OL,13,Fto Starmer's leadership of the party
OL,14,Fand country.
OL,16,FThat would lead to governmental
OL,17,Fparalysis and turmoil in bond markets
OL,18,F- even if in the end, Prime Minister
OL,19,FKeir Starmer survives.
OL,21,FBuckle up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
