OL,3,CWhy these elections are so important
OL,5,FSecond, if Reform does as well as
OL,6,Fexpected in English local elections
OL,7,Fand in Scottish and Welsh
OL,8,Fparliamentary elections, many would
OL,9,Fsee them as the real representatives
OL,10,Fof right-wing Britain.
OL,12,FThat would be a challenge to the
OL,13,Fstatus and authority of the
OL,14,FConservative Party, for all that Kemi
OL,15,FBadenoch is widely seen to be
OL,16,Fperforming effectively as their leader
OL,17,Fand they remain the official
OL,18,Fopposition in parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
