OL,3,CWhy these elections are so important
OL,5,FTalk of Reform eventually absorbing
OL,6,Fthe Tory Party, before the next
OL,7,Fgeneral election, would only intensify.
OL,9,FThird nationalist parties are like to
OL,10,Fbe in charge in the parliaments of
OL,11,FScotland, Wales and Northern Ireland:
OL,12,Fthe SNP and Plaid are almost certain
OL,13,Fto form new respective governments in
OL,14,FScotland and Wales, and Sinn Fein is
OL,15,Falready the senior partner in Northern
OL,16,FIreland's assembly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
