OL,3,CWhy these elections are so important
OL,5,FThis doesn't mean that formal break up
OL,6,Fof the UK is imminent. But if you
OL,7,Fbelieve as I do that Newton's first
OL,8,Flaw applies to politics, it means the
OL,9,Fintegrity of the UK would be much less
OL,10,Fsecure than it was.
OL,12,FFourth all the polls indicate the
OL,13,FLibDems are treading water in terms of
OL,14,Fnational vote share, and that
OL,15,Fdisillusionment with the government
OL,16,Fand Tories is disproportionately
OL,17,Fbenefiting Reform and the Greens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
