OL,3,CWhy these elections are so important
OL,5,FBy contrast and fifth, the Greens have
OL,6,Fsurged thanks in large part to the
OL,7,Fpositive charismatic force of one
OL,8,Fperson, its leader Zack Polanski.
OL,9,FWhich implies the party has a lot of
OL,10,Fpolicy work to do to consolidate its
OL,11,Fposition and be taken seriously as a
OL,12,Fpotential party of government.
OL,14,FSixth, the big story will be that
OL,15,Fthere are now at least seven parties
OL,16,Fon the British mainland - Reform, the
OL,17,FGreens, the LibDems, the SNP, Plaid
OL,18,FCymru, Labour and the Conservatives -
OL,19,Fwith legitimate claims to have
OL,20,Fmeaningful national, regional or local
OL,21,Fvote shares.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
